{"type": "article", "id": 6816, "title": "Freebinding 自定义家具", "description": "", "date": "2015-02-26T07:29:48Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 24, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606052343217DTSMXvBGcLsy8K6.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t从名字便不难看出，Freebinding 是一款创新的自定义家具产品。设计团队 BinDesign 将其制作成各个可拆卸的元件，可以完全按照使用者的需求进行组装。BinDesign 在设计的过程中以「联系」为主题，希望能够创造用户与周边环境之间或是不同用户间的联系。Freebinding 选用山毛榉曲木材质制作而成，保持其灵活又稳定的特点。为了保证用户就做时的舒适性，设计团队还在表面铺设了一层毛毡。据设计团队介绍，Freebinding 模块化易组合的特性保证了用户可以根据个人喜好与实际需求任意组合，并调整各用户之间的距离。\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234319a31qU64GJCF7AxrX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74938875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234319DyFulwafIh1MPVJX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68826406\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234320UxbBvezHAEkl7sW8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.14180929\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052343202a1Mn6jsNKQmrbuH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234320Z9huBF46RcQ5Tw28.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\n\n\n"}